Title: What's Inside Counts
Description:
I noticed something strange on my last scouting mission. A group of Zandalari are performing a ritual on what appears to be a very large sentry. They may be trying to re-animate it.

We need that ritual stopped and the sentry destroyed. Anything that large can't be good.

I've sent a scout ahead to observe their actions. Meet with her and figure out how to stop them.
ObjectivesText: Destroy Guardian Tak'u in Conqueror's Terrace.
